<button class="accordion">What does clinical and non-clinical mean?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>The term has to do with whether or not you treat patients or provide direct patient care of any type, in which case your job is clinical. Non-clinical work may support patient care, but the work does not give an immediate diagnosis, treatment, or responsibility for the patient.</p>
