<button class="accordion">How can you improve your clinical communication skills in healthcare?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Six ways healthcare leaders can improve their communications skills:</p>
<li> Choose your words carefully</li>
<li> Be clear and specific</li>
<li> Never trade clarity for inspiration</li>
<li> Don't over-specify</li>
<li> Note what is non-negotiable</li>
<li> Stretch specifications and goals can improve innovation.</li>
</div>
<button class="accordion">What are the purposes of clinical communication?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Clinical communication agrees five primary purposes: to inform, to express feelings, to imagine, to influence, and to meet social expectations. Each of these purposes is a reflection in the form of communication.</p>
